{"tid":1512693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超球隊不滿提前關窗！希望改回舊制","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:31:50.000Z","uid":103207,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"917f20e5d91275765b083f04bdbce183a3062adc","tid":1512693,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"據英國媒體《電訊報》報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">英超中的許多球會對提前關閉轉會窗口感到不滿，希望能夠改回舊的體制</span>，9月12日的股東大會上，這個議題將被提上日程。<br />\n<br />\n  英超從<span style=\"color: red;\">去年開始決定提前關閉轉會窗，在新賽季開始前關閉收購窗口</span>。但這讓英超球隊在轉會操作上變得非常困難，收購時間變短，談判相當被動。而且<span style=\"color: red;\">，英超關窗後，其他聯賽仍未關窗，可以繼續挖角英超的球員，英超球隊則無法反製</span>。<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"> 英超的各支球會將在下個月初步進行討論，有人希望能夠回到舊的制度</span>，或者希望推動其他歐霸盃也能夠和英超同一天關窗。<span style=\"color: red;\">頗為諷刺的是，當年提前關窗也是英超各隊投票後決定的</span>，如今大家又反悔了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433673b6b14c073a39a276544e3854fef559fe32","tid":1512693,"uid":89145,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7275c0d77e321344b34cc43c5f10f76d265ab7d5","tid":1512693,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=267d0364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=4f7d56c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=b87dbb0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"37129063f540490cd807c7803a3377ed02385aa2","tid":1512693,"uid":38494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 停止國泰白色恐怖 愛丁堡廣場</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見</span></strong></span> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"cac4e95021595bbb189a53f2bdd677f33ddb2dae","tid":1512693,"uid":3747,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"雲加食撚屎"},{"pid":"27bdb14668ce4c9179cb1ca11c17c4b7d41ffbc2","tid":1512693,"uid":5649,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"其實提早關轉會窗對中下游係好事"},{"pid":"302bc130ea6da8037623e1f1574facbbec158174","tid":1512693,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:56:15.000Z","msg":"哪些球隊贊成提前關窗？<br />\n<br />\n上賽季的20傢俱樂部的意見並非完全一致：有一家（伯恩利）選擇棄權，<span style=\"color: red;\">五家（曼聯、曼城、沃特福德、斯旺西和水晶宮）投了反對票</span>，但由於其餘14傢俱樂部支持提前關窗（剛好超過三分之二），因此這一提議得到了通過。<br />\n<br />\n對於英超中下游球隊而言，最大的威脅仍然來自本國聯賽內部。畢竟只有少數幾家球隊能頻繁參加歐戰，這也是為什麼大部分球隊都投了贊成票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而曼聯和曼城官方反對的理由，則在於他們認為在轉會市場上的最大威脅來自於其他歐陸豪門。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過彼時，<span style=\"color: red;\">曼市雙雄的主帥都以個人口徑表達了對提前關窗的支持態度，而深受困擾的克洛普、溫格更是提前關窗的堅定支持者</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/sports/3oapb68.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fsports%2F3oapb68.html&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=c7753903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/sports/3oapb68.html</a>"},{"pid":"352c289fae2ba767671d7242b4e4176d27c05bba","tid":1512693,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 停止國泰白色恐怖 愛丁堡廣場</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見</span></strong></span> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ad19617f995cf061060c6912c80b925934781be9","tid":1512693,"uid":57698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"一早就應該唔好整條咁on9的例"},{"pid":"3