693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ca70d9f42d424d5b8084bb1762c11a45e8b465","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e022511a29be6af69686dd7e758ef9b5e3f923f","tid":1512693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd17277b4be8015c16b1fc0d9a31a5219bc25534","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"當初就咪學人鳩投票啦猁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"高普表示：「我對於轉會窗口關閉時間並不在意，但我在意的是英超是否和其他聯賽同時關閉。<span style=\"color: red;\">我的想法是，英超想在賽季開始前關窗，這是個好主意，但只有英超這麼做，這是沒有任何意義的。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n當初投贊成嘅原因係認為英超做完 其他聯賽會跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算當年曼聯曼城史雲斯球會投反對票<br />\n摩佬 哥迪奧拿同埋Paul Clemen都出過聲話佢哋係支持提早close window<br />\n咁但係依家睇到其他聯賽唔跟 想英超徹回修例冇乜問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"除非全部聯賽同一日開League啫<br />\n唔係嘅一係就跟英超開League時間 一係點都遲過英超<br />\n兩個想法都係on9 咪扮無辜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"有幾on9講嚟聽下？<br />\n五大聯賽完league時間都係五月中到五月尾<br />\n英超個窗就5月16 開到8月8 (早開季兩日完)<br />\n法國就6月11開到9月2<br />\n西德意就7月1開到9月2<br />\n<br />\n實際上如果跟英超呢套早開早閂 其他聯賽會有更多時間轉會<br />\n跟英超個日子嘅話對法甲嚟講都係早開鑼兩日閂<br />\n對德甲西甲嚟講只係早開鑼一個星期閂<br />\n對意甲嚟講都係早開鑼兩個星期閂<br />\n<br />\n學哥迪奧拿話齋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The market finishes on August 31st. I think that&rsquo;s a huge mistake from UEFA. I think the market should finish when we start the season</span>, it&rsquo;s too long, too large. We are playing here with guys who maybe will not continue, or with players who are coming but are not here.<br />\n<br />\n摩佬都講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">I would prefer the window to close as soon as possible. So everybody knows the players we have and the deals will be done earlier and nobody would be waiting for the last week</span> and we wouldn&rsquo;t have the situation of sometimes a player plays game number one for a team and game number two for another team.<br />\n<br />\n唔通佢兩個又on9咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果五大聯賽都肯提早嘅話對領隊根本係好事<br />\n當初投票嗰陣就係想其他聯賽跟<br />\n咁依家個結果出到嚟係冇人跟 有違原本嘅諗法<br />\n嗌徹回有咩問題<br />\n喺度事後孔明叫人當初咪鳩投票 肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9ab1d0433dabd1a5ab7573d3bd594289d1133d","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afa3b43024a37ab5c1862aad7a8308e4b2a1ddd5","tid":1512693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ca70d9f42d424d5b8084bb1762c11a45e8b465","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e022511a29be6af69686dd7e758ef9b5e3f923f","tid":1512693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"高普表示：「我對於轉會窗口關閉時間並不在意，但我在意的是英超是否和其他聯賽同時關閉。<span style=\"color: red;\">我的想法是，英超想在賽季開始前關窗，這是個好主意，但只有英超這麼做，這是沒有任何意義的。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n當初投贊成嘅原因係認為英超做完 其他聯賽會跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算當年曼聯曼城史雲斯球會投反對票<br />\n摩佬 哥迪奧拿同埋Paul Clemen都出過聲話佢哋係支持提早close window<br />\n咁但係依家睇到其他聯賽唔跟 想英超徹回修例冇乜問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"除非全部聯賽同一日開League啫<br />\n唔係嘅一係就跟英超開League時間 一係點都遲過英超<br />\n兩個想法都係on9 咪扮無辜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"有幾on9講嚟聽下？<br />\n五大聯賽完league時間都係五月中到五月尾<br />\n英超個窗就5月16 開到8月8 (早開季兩日完)<br />\n法國就6月11開到9月2<br />\n西德意就7月1開到9月2<br />\n<br />\n實際上如果跟英超呢套早開早閂 其他聯賽會有更多時間轉會<br />\n跟英超個日子嘅話對法甲嚟講都係早開鑼兩日閂<br />\n對德甲西甲嚟講只係早開鑼一個星期閂<br />\n對意甲嚟講都係早開鑼兩個星期閂<br />\n<br />\n學哥迪奧拿話齋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The market finishes on August 31st. I think that&rsquo;s a huge mistake from UEFA. I think the market should finish when we start the season</span>, it&rsquo;s too long, too large. We are playing here with guys who maybe will not continue, or with players who are coming but are not here.<br />\n<br />\n摩佬都講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">I would prefer the window to close as soon as possible. So everybody knows the players we have and the deals will be done earlier and nobody would be waiting for the last week</span> and we wouldn&rsquo;t have the situation of sometimes a player plays game number one for a team and game number two for another team.<br />\n<br />\n唔通佢兩個又on9咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果五大聯賽都肯提早嘅話對領隊根本係好事<br />\n當初投票嗰陣就係想其他聯賽跟<br />\n咁依家個結果出到嚟係冇人跟 有違原本嘅諗法<br />\n嗌徹回有咩問題<br />\n喺度事後孔明叫人當初咪鳩投票 肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"邊個事後孔明想撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKlopp: He refused to comment on Lovren&rsquo;s future but said: &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t care when it closes, but it must close at the same time. That was the idea in the first place. They spoke about finishing it before the season starts, good idea, but only England did it. That makes no sense.<br />\n<br />\n佢係想「同一刻Close」呀老闆<br />\n係咪要五大聯賽集中同一日開League呀？<br />\n咁唔係嘅話點同一日呀？<br />\n另一個可能要全世界就英超開鑼日之前關？咁使唔使就埋歐霸淘汰賽？投之前有無用腦呀？"},{"pid":"aac29b6f604b0b04023b96f50b00782e8494aaac","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"再補充<br />\n哥狗同摩佬覺得同一日關/早d關 係好 同高普諗法一樣<br />\n但唔會投贊成就係因為知道人哋聯賽唔會跟你英超丫嘛<br />\n咁投贊成嗰個係咪唔撚用腦呀猁狗？<br />\n我唔係覺得開League要關轉會窗on9<br />\n係投贊成票覺得全世界會跟住行on9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 教猁狗好似教小學生咁"},{"pid":"f12f7fdfa340ea9b0c15cc0497603438d73891f4","tid":1512693,"uid":226671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idpo1ti.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fidpo1ti.png&h=c65e5f22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2a6ce6accb3141c9ddbfe06c3c5d1a9ae803c5f","tid":1512693,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"或者希望推動其他歐霸盃也能夠和英超同一天關窗。<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得獌要踢歐霸<br />\n方便大曬金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd1631c7260dae074179a3232303a332d47fae6","tid":1512693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e9ab1d0433dabd1a5ab7573d3bd594289d1133d","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afa3b43024a37ab5c1862aad7a8308e4b2a1ddd5","tid":1512693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ca70d9f42d424d5b8084bb1762c11a45e8b465","tid":1512693,"uid":14238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"除非全部聯賽同一日開League啫<br />\n唔係嘅一係就跟英超開League時間 一係點都遲過英超<br />\n兩個想法都係on9 咪扮無辜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"有幾on9講嚟聽下？<br />\n五大聯賽完league時間都係五月中到五月尾<br />\n英超個窗就5月16 開到8月8 (早開季兩日完)<br />\n法國就6月11開到9月2<br />\n西德意就7月1開到9月2<br />\n<br />\n實際上如果跟英超呢套早開早閂 其他聯賽會有更多時間轉會<br />\n跟英超個日子嘅話對法甲嚟講都係早開鑼兩日閂<br />\n對德甲西甲嚟講只係早開鑼一個星期閂<br />\n對意甲嚟講都係早開鑼兩個星期閂<br />\n<br />\n學哥迪奧拿話齋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The market finishes on August 31st. I think that&rsquo;s a huge mistake from UEFA. I think the market should finish when we start the season</span>, it&rsquo;s too long, too large. We are playing here with guys who maybe will not continue, or with players who are coming but are not here.<br />\n<br />\n摩佬都講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">I would prefer the window to close as soon as possible. So everybody knows the players we have and the deals will be done earlier and nobody would be waiting for the last week</span> and we wouldn&rsquo;t have the situation of sometimes a player plays game number one for a team and game number two for another team.<br />\n<br />\n唔通佢兩個又on9咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果五大聯賽都肯提早嘅話對領隊根本係好事<br />\n當初投票嗰陣就係想其他聯賽跟<br />\n咁依家個結果出到嚟係冇人跟 有違原本嘅諗法<br />\n嗌徹回有咩問題<br />\n喺度事後孔明叫人當初咪鳩投票 肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"邊個事後孔明想撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKlopp: He refused to comment on Lovren&rsquo;s future but said: &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t care when it closes, but it must close at the same time. That was the idea in the first place. They spoke about finishing it before the season starts, good idea, but only England did it. That makes no sense.<br />\n<br />\n佢係想「同一刻Close」呀老闆<br />\n係咪要五大聯賽集中同一日開League呀？<br />\n咁唔係嘅話點同一日呀？<br />\n另一個可能要全世界就英超開鑼日之前關？咁使唔使就埋歐霸淘汰賽？投之前有無用腦呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"你明唔明事後孔明係咩意思?<br />\nklopp個諗法一路冇變過 都係想提早close 只不過係最後其他聯賽唔跟所以先話撤回<br />\n邊度事後孔明?<br />\n你依家喺投票過咗兩年之後睇到晒個結果 見到冇人跟 然後批評佢當初投票 呢啲就真係事後孔明喇<br />\n<br />\n同埋同一刻close關歐霸乜撚嘢事?<br />\n上年意甲都試過提早close一個星期 同英超都係爭三日close<br />\n呢啲嘢跟本有慢慢協調 但你唔做就一定冇人跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895feea1d9aa0fea3c17537ebd6ffcb4612b1309","tid":1512693,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aac29b6